    "project_template_level_name": "CSA U7L4-L1 Private PBT_alt-2025",
    "teacher_markdown": "Students will see the following error displayed in the console:\r\n\r\n```\r\n/RecipeRunner.java:17: error: recipesToString(Recipe,Recipe) has private access in RecipeBlog\r\n    System.out.println(\"Recommended vegetarian recipes:\\n\" + blog.recipesToString(r2, r3));\r\n                                                                 ^\r\n```\r\nSince the `recipesToString()` method is a `private` method, it can only be accessed within the `RecipeBlog` class.",
